:0}}],\"rating\":4.1,\"reviews\":[{\"author_name\":\"JM Wu\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103120049954902781641/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUL81FvXyLxYsd8etjcPKBP8oM6uqEE4RGv2bHs6kE3xotX3Hy-=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"2 週前\",\"text\":\"一間開了很久的老店，\\n很久前來吃過一次，印象中烤鴨跟湯都不錯！\\n這次再來吃果然還是一樣的好味道~\\n來這邊一定要點烤鴨和酸菜白肉鍋！\\n另外還有一道鴨酥蠻特別的，裡面還有茡薺（連不喜歡吃茡薺的朋友都覺得蠻好吃的）\\n還有最後甜點：芋頭薄餅，熱熱的吃濃郁的芋頭香跟薄薄的餅也蠻特別的~\\n有來到新竹可以來這間試嚐看看喔！\\n晚上18：30開始大概20：00就開始收了喔！\\n所以是同事聚餐好選擇~（上菜也很快，不會吃到太晚喔！\\n\\nPS:喜歡我的評論可以追蹤喔~\\n將現場看到食物的樣子及色調拍攝下來呈現給大家，會到各地去發掘美食及特色地點喔！！\\n祝大家心想事成喔！🥳\",\"time\":1747929133,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"young\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108270117539374476355/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdSDUHNavo0UvVhPARHrS_j2Zd6fZ-Bcxx2xbVRRbPaoKjioDr=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 個月前\",\"text\":\"人均約500-600左右，比較適合至少5人以上聚餐，停車不方便，附近只有一個小收費停車場🅿️。\\n\\n上菜非常快，通常不需等待太久，但老闆很想早點下班的心情很明顯😂😂\\n\\n烤鴨很好吃～推推，記得要先點，菜點完基本上就不太給續點，記得一次點完🤣🤣\\n\\n東西都滿不錯的，就是適合聚餐的中式餐點店，環境比較老舊，但東西真的好吃。\\n\\n芋泥餅跟鳳梨蝦球也好吃，酸菜白肉鍋一鍋大概4-5人份而已，建議多點一些料來配👍\\n\\n偏推薦，但老闆20:30要準時打烊，所以記得早點到～～通常平日不太需要訂位，但都可以訂位，怕沒位置還是訂位比較方便。\",\"time\":1746094365,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Chang Huei Chen\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109886674499281979859/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJt0Fo-2LZp-dOIO4Wi5f8DGp44QRqQqcrmt2BSeZTyqWzOFw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"2 週前\",\"text\":\"家庭聚餐，烤鴨、酸白菜鍋必點！烤鴨建議點滿吃發~鄰近停車場比較少，要早點找車位~吃午餐但菜品僅能點一次不能加點比較可惜！\",\"time\":1747738644,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Sunny Chuang\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113462572601534221459/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZCj9869hCTL68Yf-VtXkPif5IKPWMX0MAzcUItBaJcvxc-A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":1,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 個月前\",\"text\":\"內用大概5次左右，外帶也差不多。\\n周六晚上去吃，整個超錯愕，變很不好吃，\\n烤鴨皮過乾，吃起來乾又有油耗味，\\n肉也是很硬，完全沒有之前的水準，超失望，這次吃起來比外面街上烤鴨店還差。\\n連甜麵醬都變很鹹。\\n\\n山蘇 調味鹹到一口需要配一碗飯的感覺。\\n高麗菜和蝦仁烘蛋算正常好吃。\\n黃金豆腐是坊間金沙豆腐稍油但也不錯吃。\\n一吃是炒韭黃，鴨肉這邊是嫩的好吃。\\n二吃炒鴨骨，跟外面烤鴨店差不多。\\n\\n內用抵消3000元。\\n\\n碗盤使用痕跡過重，內用環境不優。\\n\\n男店員態度差。\\n\\n希望老店的好要傳承不要越來越差。\",\"time\":1744564525,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Sean He\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109745553639958486808/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzV3Kcg0kLEDGioj4pOr2S7ZTJCp4eFQR7RuTkTFDwfdE_Nyo62w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":3,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 個月前\",\"text\":\"個人覺得挺普通的，主打的北京烤鴨與酸菜白肉鍋都沒有特別亮眼，沒有太特別的記憶點，比較推薦的是軟殼蟹與鳳梨蝦球，cp值不高\",\"time\":1745390761,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNSGSZQDXOo6hyX3Byd8gu-EGZbrAY27oV77S9SR-X0BdEg63dFzDoG1S3FqhOCpTI5Q6U2q7DufaxHNkgVUIOib3D2B9PaIXOt5AuUd3XM_bZvearIhW8S0R8wq2yG7tBB9m6ZSMrFjRJpCcAUWbTMq3gZ0TVNm1s6Q0-97TYLE6Q3cvwqWEN9uaOC7XGuyKxJUyacifvgwfpg--IW86onjhJfdbD_Ykfbbli2FYJjbgRstunkR7a8RDK53il4_xSORA9kajQmYzMQC4v6H3O8QmbeEWlzT76qc9b5hsnuZa7WuX2yWLDdV2ZySJprtNM8C2_oxg0ZTh166GyPoRf3rqjOPSjMTrU8jMiAtzu5-N874OeH5wTIlLsOrbw_0CCVzwRyY6D7VGr_YNvxuc72ijNDiYf20I8hhZbz-8VhHyAWMnjnLAe4yAK8lUd31wP8kQh1nSIn3hp2e9QePh2-apfnkhwbM_VlhHp17paRHTj1O3HS4iHnNWMQijCkxnrqUgv_0XpdXQ62gAFdWu7tYxlgjzMhW4JantI3wVxUWKIJuR6X3-6Epltgbw_-87eKaR2IddMs9u733VI4A7IpBCKuot9bOi7N7amuK6Mo2dbMjwNPxT6PUUhKW2zSmrq29XA\",\"AXQCQNSUyAN6R0eAVPP7ypihNNBC6NdPaaA1OsVdHjb5SmkKVwCJU1IzoCy7-wg9Ib0jaRQj-HUk5jbEZ0RKwG8rqUJSSyI66-24loOLswUjiyQlODbvtrP3iysvSTKLi7vn0N2ZHXmlFt1AfXoLiOJdvV_jU94CdrNkuecAz0UlWU1lcj45urMSuQtrahUhikb7wyOMkkGrwxwaQeNnrjr7aMy2F087VmLtg93CNskoxhEQTj5KAlPYbzE1op302RdZ_ujBNlokk3K_tq1R3dgONTv6UiwKlTt03-eqeJ1oml2mMK1JGYvXUqCvBI5SIt