:10,\"minute\":50},\"end\":{\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}}],\"rating\":4.5,\"reviews\":[{\"author_name\":\"Huel\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107740564900561259818/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCPm6Sift3cMRoZ6HBLFDzBQZOHEjioJSsbuNDNS5EHlte1w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"2 週前\",\"text\":\"莧菜鍋氣很讚😎😎😎\\nㄧ口接一口😋😋😋\\n服務員適時的來加茶😉😉😉\\n增加了用餐的舒適度\\n讓餐點覺得更加好消化\\n麻醬麵麵條很好吃醬就一般\\n糙米飯出乎意料的炒的很好吃\\n很推薦👍👍👍\",\"time\":1747908900,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Emilee\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110547819516503187515/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXdD788a7uyV00dOIIdbE8sTf7-B7cujkqn-w6bXhzDkZgfdTURw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":2,\"relative_time_description\":\"2 個月前\",\"text\":\"漲太多但品質沒有跟上\\n小籠湯包太油膩\\n蝦仁紅油炒手內餡很空不飽滿\\n巧克力小包、雪菜麵跟牛肉麵表現平平\\n炒飯跟酸辣湯ok\\n\\n整體而言，是平淡的一餐\",\"time\":1742916593,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"YuRu Chen\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115298789530008518559/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvh1pyVzm0RcRKBzWjnK2cl4hFRvQNE8Lb4sf6GgmfiVpGq2lFAw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 個月前\",\"text\":\"每次來都一定點小籠包跟炒飯，最常點蝦仁炒飯再來是排骨炒飯，鼎泰豐每一道都好吃不踩雷可以放心點餐\\n服務好、乾淨食材新鮮、餐點好吃…鼎泰豐絕對是用餐好選擇。\",\"time\":1745684359,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Judy Chu\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107405539300305305651/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJvMOEzGquptc61xXXqrZkkcOa1zq_hMrGTpZrAYydZF6l6jKI=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"5 個月前\",\"text\":\"遠百地下一樓的餐廳，餐點都維持在很棒的水準，沒有雷的，店員服務也很周到👍\\n小籠包還是最喜歡原味，絲瓜蝦仁和蔬食個人感覺還可以，口味比較清淡。紹興醉雞的酒味恰到好處，推薦可以嘗試看看。甜點的話，松糕也很不錯，軟糯又有點嚼勁，不會太甜。\",\"time\":1735043191,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"陳名麒\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100915151539228785021/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXB3yPY-KHIg2aiyqArrtsNHIue4L16ssmXNlSGkpz3yllVGDjd=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"4 個月前\",\"text\":\"久久沒吃味道、服務依舊，鼎泰豐的服務就是讓人放心，味道也是沒走味過，不愧是SOP名店。以假日晚間用餐來說，18:10左右拿號碼牌接近一小時才入店，餐廳在地下一樓尖峰時段非常擁擠，可以到附近閒逛掃QR code查叫號狀態，或者19:15後拿號碼牌等候時間會更短且排到的位置會更大。\\n\\n這次兩人用餐除了每次必點的三件套排骨蛋炒飯、小籠包、蝦肉紅油炒手外，還試了糖醋排骨、菠菜、蝦肉煎餃、巧克力小籠包，吃完後直接飽到天靈蓋。蛋炒飯加紅油炒手一生推推，小籠包吃來吃去自己還是最愛原味，冬天建議上菜後要快點吃完，涼掉後變得普普，當中最特別的是巧克力小籠包，外皮雖薄卻有嚼勁，再搭配趁熱吃可以吃到的爆漿巧克力內餡，有種中式大福的感覺，也推薦點來試試看。\",\"time\":1736673699,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNRyhGkZHPZKrm-EDNZqsYn2uXxLjCkgsNT6eRdPjPIBZJ7Xgr89ybRX2_et4zAilKet6599xQHfeS6swu4emdWhlIS3YXic77xnmGSPP4PxOlmRqflc16o8lOvDBzM34Mcj-ARpNKrsqkPVzSJWmvw95xqZnZpByxKXW-FSzbT3wgRxLr3uycC08ZmlwFo3vlCOKNjaplC_DiEoZPEqoCmQ9e5g7IvYSbtVUgUglr_7hytQe_ENs73ZdEzVNX5xhpiCttaP8HVocxtE42AI7A2HyJY2USIMPxk1t1_21yv0wFEo6_4RvnJAspCoPPX6onxs5prRCVow9YoDIsVp9t3DF5ejaKCEsHtnzPFNhFV7-2bPKXnNrDOWmZ0cvm1tkmN2FbgcvuW-Kwg31jyNQ3XfGgLZjZIwgCM6J8oaUbvYhdep7oHeN_Umnr_MPVcJPwYWEcVnIdX5zbuJzkNhPL2MXs7yqgjWBuCfq__QHU3AEbj9XuNnx7cVYbbSLRflm5odq9Oih6wMGRc_BG5FHnH1Qu0wNMhcPlJOjAGny5c43Np2rTjBjM2EcMUNLuOKApNdPTIGbvFVrvSfQ-D3gOD6hfCI2Zf-_JHwjFdgRobc5fFudWw75AAGH8sqhxlC\",\"AXQCQNSw9jJUWqeh_2MmTUoIHJW-IpHNDVJ__oPSfr9boLqm9WscQ2STeSAd5gY25eUc-DUAGY_LJWe6g6Gge_oAWoLQTp67oA6qo4B75uJcYBoMqYR2tNYR0fYy7eHu33ksVb_qaHhmhPz8LhgtA9tAA7cWI0KdpiE0S_6-VlPVr-TNsOFj4ksqOx06QNlzwKaS02sUWhHmn0X4AlqgXC0a3mAg9ttnMhYj13u6kqYb-oxA5WWCDnyPG9LKH_FEJvQin2fa7jKN2nsIdQL8j_x0JnIqYDNN0zuQPyghOTV8kbl-KUWSmohkpFzkpNpeCwLnsyBaacBpn5BnXlV4XXhglWBMqZ6ptH6gIPdiluXX7U_QiBzN3DQfac0KJ6KlRmHgTn3wDHDuSMiCaM4Ho4xf27lgDz6_DqC0T5tYN4fP1PkGWujvxnAIE2LtsMYfiiw5oO5Zg_a2eArMfsk_YhrMc09LZPdfqzbni--yapi4M2iOKfKd3w4IAHbYzhwZNuwQjw5AylPvrheq8wsHNvqQUtvY9KxQj5m-Dmnt3Xn8nK77Synxc